item.title: What do i do with the md5?
item.dc:creator: NeedHelpGuy
item.description:
DaftMink:

It’s not vital to the install process so don’t worry about it.
Just a check to make sure the files not corrupt which unless your download stopped it shouldn’t be.

A good program for md5 checks is QuickSFV though.

thanks for letting me know! another thing is it says that a lot of the files need to go into an archive.How do i do that?
